            "body": "> Probably need to add status command to each config.\n\nNo. If server commands can't be bothered to provide `--version`, we aren't going to maintain special workarounds for them. They can either provide `--version` or we will report \"failed to get version\". It is idiotic that they don't provide `--version`, or some other common arg to get version/status info.",
