            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Something I'd like to see is whether an LSP has document formatting support. I have a `BufWritePre` hook that will format the buffer using all available LSPs. Sometimes that doesn't behave in the way I want (e.g. conflicting styles) so I'd like to know which LSPs are being triggered.\n\nI'm not sure this should be included in lspconfig or if a new API should exist to allow end-users to configure additional status functions to be ran for all language servers.",
